#. type: Content of: <h1>
#: en/10_welcome.html:1
msgid "Welcome to Linux Mint Debian"
msgstr "Benvinguts"

#. type: Content of: <div><div><ul><li>
#: en/10_welcome.html:6
msgid "Thank you for choosing Linux Mint."
msgstr "Gràcies per triar Linux Mint"

#. type: Content of: <div><div><ul><li>
#: en/10_welcome.html:7
msgid ""
"We believe in sharing and being open-minded. Our vision of Freedom includes "
"being able to do what you want with your computer, and the operating system "
"should never stand in the way."
msgstr ""
"Creiem en compartir i ser oberts. La nostra visió de la Llibertat és que "
"hauríeu de ser capaç de fer el que volguéssiu amb el vostre ordinador, i el "
"vostre sistema operatiu hauria d'ajudar-vos a aconseguir precisament això."

#. type: Content of: <div><div><ul><li>
#: en/10_welcome.html:8
msgid ""
"We focus on ease of use, comfort, and elegance to make your experience with "
"Linux Mint as enjoyable as possible."
msgstr ""
"Ens centrem en la facilitat d'ús, la comoditat i l'elegància perquè pugueu "
"gaudir al màxim de la vostra experiència amb l'escriptori de Linux Mint."

#. type: Content of: <div><div><p>
#: en/10_welcome.html:11
msgid ""
"We hope you will have a wonderful time spent with Linux Mint, and that you "
"will enjoy using it as much as we do developing it!"
msgstr ""
"Desitgem que ho passeu esplèndidament amb Linux Mint i que gaudiu tant en "
"usar-lo com nosaltres en desenvolupar-lo!"

#. type: Content of: <h1>
#: en/20_giants.html:1
msgid "Standing on the shoulders of Giants"
msgstr "Sobre les espatlles de gegants"

#. type: Content of: <div><div><ul><li>
#: en/20_giants.html:6
msgid "Linux Mint is a Debian-based GNU/Linux distribution."
msgstr "Linux Mint és una distribució GNU/Linux basada en Debian"

#. type: Content of: <div><div><ul><li>
#: en/20_giants.html:7
msgid ""
"Our innovations and the huge Debian package selection make Linux Mint one of "
"the most attractive desktop operating systems available to home users."
msgstr ""
"Les nostres innovacion i la gran selecció de paquets de Debian fan de Linux "
"Mint un dels sistemes operatius d'escriptori més atractius disponible per "
"als usuaris domèstics."

#. type: Content of: <div><div><ul><li>
#: en/20_giants.html:8
#, fuzzy
#| msgid ""
#| "At home, Linux Mint is the 4th most widely used desktop operating system, "
#| "behind Microsoft Windows, Apple OS X and Ubuntu."
msgid ""
"At home, GNU/Linux distributions like Linux Mint or Ubuntu are among the "
"most widely used desktop operating systems, right next to Microsoft Windows "
"and Apple OS X."
msgstr ""
"A la llar, Linux Mint és el quart sistema operatiu més utilitzat, per "
"darrere de Microsoft Windows, Apple OS X i Ubuntu."

#. type: Content of: <h1>
#: en/30_desktop-ready.html:1
msgid "Out of the box"
msgstr "Llest per a usar"

#. type: Content of: <div><div><ul><li>
#: en/30_desktop-ready.html:6
#, fuzzy
#| msgid ""
#| "Firefox, Thunderbird, OpenOffice.org and Xchat come pre-installed in "
#| "Linux Mint, so you can get started immediately with your daily routine on "
#| "your desktop and the Internet."
msgid ""
"Most standard applications you are used to come pre-installed in Linux Mint, "
"so you can get started immediately with your daily routine on your desktop "
"and the Internet."
msgstr ""
"Firefox, Thunderbird, OpenOffice.org i Xchat venen preinstal·lats amb Linux "
"Mint, de manera que podeu començar immediatament a utilitzar l'escriptori i "
"l'Internet."

#. type: Content of: <div><div><ul><li>
#: en/30_desktop-ready.html:7
#, fuzzy
#| msgid ""
#| "Other popular applications such as Skype, Google Earth, Opera can be "
#| "installed with a click of the mouse."
msgid ""
"Other popular applications such as Skype, Google Earth, Opera, and over "
"30,000+ more can be installed with a click of the mouse."
msgstr ""
"Altres aplicacions populars com Skype, Google Earth o Opera poden instal·lar-"
"se amb un clic de ratolí."

#. type: Content of: <div><div><ul><li>
#: en/30_desktop-ready.html:8
msgid ""
"Linux Mint is compatible with most popular file formats: zip, doc, xls, pdf, "
"rar, mp3, wmv, mpg, mp4, mov ..."
msgstr ""
"Linux Mint és compatible amb els formats d'arxiu més populars: zip, doc, "
"xls, pdf, rar, mp3, wmv, mpg, mp4, mov ..."

#. type: Content of: <h1>
#: en/40_office.html:1
msgid "Be productive"
msgstr "Sigueu productius"

#. type: Content of: <div><div><ul><li>
#: en/40_office.html:6
msgid ""
"Use LibreOffice to create professional documents, spreadsheets and "
"presentations that are fully compatible with Microsoft Office. Share "
"printers or access them remotely."
msgstr ""
"Amb LibreOffice podeu crear documents professionals, fulls de càlcul i "
"presentacions plenament compatibles amb Microsoft Office. Compartiu "
"impressores o accediu-hi remotament."

#. type: Content of: <h1>
#: en/50_windows.html:1
msgid "An alternative to mainstream operating systems"
msgstr "Una alternativa als principals sistemes operatius"

#. type: Content of: <div><div><ul><li>
#: en/50_windows.html:6
msgid "Linux Mint is easy to use, powerful and configurable."
msgstr "Linux Mint és fàcil d'usar, potent i configurable."

#. type: Content of: <div><div><ul><li>
#: en/50_windows.html:7
msgid ""
"Linux Mint can detect other operating systems and install itself beside "
"them. You can choose which operating system to launch when you start the "
"computer."
msgstr ""
"Linux Mint pot detectar altres sistemes operatius i instal·lar-se juntament "
"amb ells. Pots triar quin sistema operatiu s'executa en iniciar l'equip."

#. type: Content of: <div><div><ul><li>
#: en/50_windows.html:8
#, fuzzy
#| msgid ""
#| "Install Wine and run Windows software in Linux Mint. Or install "
#| "Virtualbox, and run Windows itself within Linux Mint."
msgid ""
"Install Wine and run Windows software in Linux Mint. Or install VirtualBox, "
"and run Windows itself within Linux Mint."
msgstr ""
"Instal·leu Wine i executeu programari de Windows a Linux Mint. O instal·leu "
"Virtualbox i executeu Windows mateix dins de Linux Mint."

#. type: Content of: <h1>
#: en/60_safe.html:1
msgid "Safe updates"
msgstr "Actualitzacions segures"

#. type: Content of: <div><div><ul><li>
#: en/60_safe.html:6
msgid ""
"Linux Mint is safe and stable, you don't need an antivirus, an anti-spyware, "
"a defragmentation tool or a registry cleaner."
msgstr ""
"Linux Mint és segur i estable, no necessiteu antivirus, anti-programari "
"espia, eines de desfragmentació o netejadors del registre."

#. type: Content of: <div><div><ul><li>
#: en/60_safe.html:7
msgid ""
"Receive fixes and security updates all in one place, for the entire system, "
"including the software you install."
msgstr ""
"Rebeu solucions a problemes i actualitzacions al mateix lloc, per al sistema "
"sencer, incloent el programari que instal·leu."

#. type: Content of: <div><div><ul><li>
#: en/60_safe.html:8
msgid ""
"The Linux Mint Update Manager sits discreetly in your system tray and lets "
"you know when updates are available. You don't have to apply updates when "
"you don't want to. The Update Manager won't pop up or annoy you in any way."
msgstr ""
"El Gestor d'Actualitzacions de Linux Mint romandrà a la safata de sistema i "
"us avisarà quan hi hagi actualitzacions disponibles. No cal que apliqueu les "
"actualitzacions si no ho voleu. El Gestor d'Actualitzacions no mostrarà "
"finestres emergents ni molestarà de cap altra manera."

#. type: Content of: <h1>
#: en/70_chat.html:1
msgid "Stay connected"
msgstr "Mantingueu-vos connectats"

#. type: Content of: <div><div><ul><li>
#: en/70_chat.html:6
msgid ""
"Keep in touch with your friends and contacts, by email, messenger or on your "
"favorite social networks. Linux Mint provides all you need to interact with "
"Twitter, Facebook, Google Hangouts, ICQ, IRC, AIM, Yahoo and many other "
"networks."
msgstr ""
"Romaneu en contacte amb els vostres amics i coneguts per email, messenger o "
"en les vostres xarxes socials preferides. Linux Mint inclou tot el que "
"necessiteu per a interactuar amb Twitter, Facebook, Google Hangouts, ICQ, "
"IRC, AIM, Yahoo i moltes altres xarxes."

#. type: Content of: <h1>
#: en/80_community.html:1
msgid "A great community"
msgstr "Una gran comunitat"

#. type: Content of: <div><div><ul><li>
#: en/80_community.html:6
msgid ""
"The Linux Mint community is one of the best on the Internet. Our users not "
"only provide most of our funding, but also ideas, artwork, and sometimes "
"even source code."
msgstr ""
"La comunitat de Linux Mint és una de les millors a l'Internet. Els nostres "
"usuaris proporcionen la major part del nostre finançament, però també idees, "
"dissenys i de vegades fins i tot codi font."

#. type: Content of: <div><div><ul><li>
#: en/80_community.html:7
msgid ""
"Linux Mint users are happy to share their passion, enthusiasm, and eagerness "
"to help. Don't hesitate to ask questions in the forums or get involved with "
"the community."
msgstr ""
"Generalment, els usuaris de Linux Mint s'alegren de poder compartir la seva "
"passió i el seu entusiasme i estan disposats a ajudar. No dubteu a fer "
"preguntes als fòrums o a involucrar-vos amb la comunitat."

#. type: Content of: <div><div><ul><li>
#: en/80_community.html:8
msgid ""
"Send us your feedback and tell us about your experience. We'll listen to "
"your ideas and use them to further improve Linux Mint."
msgstr ""
"Envieu-nos els vostres comentaris i conteu-nos la vostra experiència. "
"Escoltarem les vostres idees i les usarem per a millorar Linux Mint."
